creator: E-MetroTel
descriptionHtml:
Do you do business on the go? Leverage the communication power of your E-MetroTel UCx with a Fully Featured Softphone combined with a Mobility, Video, Presence, and Public/Private Chat solution.

Stay integrated to your office and co-workers with the InfinityOne Mobile Client. Make and receive telephone calls to and from anyone using all the same breadth of capabilities you would from your fully featured XStim® based Infinity office desktop phone with the same user interface. E-MetroTel’s InfinityOne mobile client allows you to be fully integrated into your UCx office communications wherever you are. Log in as an agent in your company Call Center using a Bluetooth headset. Place your desktop phone call on hold, pick up your mobile device, and continue the call as you run to your next appointment.

Chat and collaborate directly with specific individuals or all your team via public or private group messages and share important documents or photos with office workers from wherever you need to be in the field just like Slack. InfinityOne helps you stay connected while social distancing by allowing you to create and participate in video conferences with screen sharing with co-workers and customers alike.

Enjoy the freedom of mobility with the knowledge that all your internal corporate communication and messaging is secure on your own private UCx system, whether it is physically in your office or in the cloud!

Features:
- Seamless telephony integration with E-MetroTel UCx call servers via our patented XStim protocol
- Tap a posted phone number or someone's phone icon to call them
- Receive incoming phone calls when your phone is locked
- Single button access to start of connect to a video conference
- Connect to others using Direct Messages, Public Rooms, or Private Chats
- Securely share files, photos or video
- See who's online or on the phone with separate chat and phone status icons

This application requires an E-MetroTel UCx system with a configured InfinityOne Server.
